Electric Six - I Shall Exterminate Everything Around Me That Restricts Me From Being The Master [2007]

The fourth album by the Detroit rock band Electric Six. After the two kick-ass albums "Fire" and "Senor Smoke" (it&#039;s better not to mention the crappy "Switzerland") this is the fourth album of the crazy rock band Electric Six.
